Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:07.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live in a world of peace\NWithout conflict, like the one I dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:20.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be patient any longer\NThere are things I must say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:23.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At the evening bus stop\Non the way home
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:26.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I Wave to those sunken shoulders,\NBye Bye Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:32.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Got to show your Fighting Pose, Oh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:38.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That world I dreamed of\NIs peaceful every day, without any conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:40.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthere are troubles every day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:44.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes I regret,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:55.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lies probably have little meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:01:02.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,~All my loving\NOtherwise, how can I go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:09.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Sweet Love I dreamed of\NWhere lovers search for a hideaway
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.48,0:01:12.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthe days we can't meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:16.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go on; but we still believe,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:25.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We may stumble, but Way to go!!\NYeah!! Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:28.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A mud-caked Rolling star!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.34,0:01:48.31,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,DEPARTMENT OF\NRESEARCH AND DEVELOPMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:42.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that we'd be\Nguarding a place like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:43.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of bizarre things
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:46.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in the Department of Research\Nand Development.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.53,0:01:49.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Seems there are a number of\Ndangerous tools in there, as well…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.37,0:01:51.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:54.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.92,0:01:59.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:06.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A ryoka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:11.01,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,DEPARTMENT OF\NRESEARCH AND DEVELOPMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:13.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a fine day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:32.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:33.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.73,0:02:39.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant, what could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:47.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But something with immense energy\Nis coming this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:50.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:52.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the ryoka has invaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:54.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to intercept them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:26.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is\Nthis Spiritual Pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's different from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:31.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… It's difficult to tell
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:33.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,because of all the battles\Nhappening around us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:36.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but one of the Bounts’\Npresences disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a different one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:41.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:43.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Kariya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:50.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So he's finally come out…\NWhich way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:51.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:52.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:54.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:56.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.16,0:03:57.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:03:59.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:02.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You sense the Bount, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:05.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… It's Kariya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:07.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:08.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:18.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anyone good around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:20.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:21.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nieder!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:23.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:42.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Quincy boy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:04.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! What an obnoxious boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:34.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you're luring me in…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:53.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:58.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you give up\Non revenge already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:01.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:04.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?\NWhy are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:07.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is no meaning to this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For that matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:15.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,aren't Quincies and Soul Reapers\Nsupposed to be enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:19.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you allying yourself\Nwith the Soul Reapers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.47,0:06:23.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not allying myself\Nwith the Soul Reapers…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:27.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to stop pointless battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:30.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're not making any sense…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:37.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will put an end to this battle\Non my pride as a Quincy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:41.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:44.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to die so badly,\Nthen just do as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:49.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rantao…you know about\NIshida's artifact, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:52.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How long will it hold up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:59.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It may become useless today…\NIt may be tomorrow…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:01.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If it goes off accidentally…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:02.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It may blow away everything…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:07.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,within a radius of\Nseveral thousand meters…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:12.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I made up my mind…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:17.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do this,\Nno matter what happens…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:24.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow them to roam freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:27.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:29.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:37.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is my true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hyapponjin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hyapponjin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:40.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:40.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My, my… That wasn't good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:49.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:52.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped…\NHe’s just a boy…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:55.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:55.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:04.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my. You're pretty fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:14.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you stop fusing with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:15.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:20.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I hate being physically fused with you\Nthroughout the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:23.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:25.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:29.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you going to do,\NQuincy Boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:34.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With that kind of attack,\NI can only dodge at best…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:36.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:40.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not coming,\Nthen I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:47.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty gentle attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:53.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! What a time for\Nme to lose power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:57.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to before…\Nit's definitely unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:08:59.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If it’s like this,\Nthere’s no point even if it hits…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:07.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My power went negative\Non my third attack…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:10.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it hardly\Nhad any power…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:12.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When I release…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:14.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When my energy\Nbecomes positive,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:18.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that's when I have the power\Nto destroy my opponent…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:19.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:26.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,when that energy\Nswings towards positive…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:31.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This arrow will be triggered\Nand blow away everything around it…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:35.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it will also blow away\Nthe person who fired it…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.17,0:09:37.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:39.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the long face?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:40.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you brooding about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:46.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can I do this? Is it possible\Nfor me to control this arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:50.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No! I've got to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:11.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That should…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:20.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:25.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is my true form!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:28.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I boast perfect protection\Nin this form!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:32.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your attacks are now meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:32.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your attacks are now meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:57.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that arrow's power\Nis different every time…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:01.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, he can't control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:05.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But if I didn't come out just now…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:07.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it would have been a bit close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:09.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop with the blasé explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:15.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn… Just when I was able\Nto fire at high power…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:20.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No. Don't give up.\NI mustn't forget this feeling…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:23.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And keep on firing…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:28.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:54.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:05.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hit…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:08.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hit…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:09.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:13.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a fool…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:16.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Using a weapon that\Nhe can't even control…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:24.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Say…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Say…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:55.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you really want to fight me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:55.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you really want to fight me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:57.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,bring a better weapon now, won’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:57.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,bring a better weapon now, won’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really. What a fool…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:09.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're naive…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:24.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where…are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:28.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There should be\Na Bount Crest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:31.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Crest?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:36.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The original.\NThe first crest created…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.32,0:13:41.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've never even heard\Nof that crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:48.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not asking you where it is.\NI just came to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:53.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do\Nonce you get it, Kariya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:57.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:02.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This man…He's dangerous…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:07.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know… I know that\Na lot better than you do…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:12.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya! What do you plan to do\Nwith this crest you’re talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:16.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Defeat me if you wish to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:21.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:26.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:27.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:33.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:37.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:41.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the crest that\Nhe's searching for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:46.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry…\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:49.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we don't know\Nwhere it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:51.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we can just follow\NKariya's Spiritual Pressure…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:53.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:54.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's resonating!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like it's in this room…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:45.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:49.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:52.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:08.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tensa Zangetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:24.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you do as you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:26.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:31.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to deal with you before\NI can take my time to look for the crest…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:45.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:53.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:12.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:14.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,keep beating me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:32.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:41.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is…\NI never thought it was in here…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:51.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was hidden in\Na place like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:32.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the crest\NI was searching for!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:41.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mein wappen,\Nunter der erde schläft!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.69,0:18:46.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Vereinige sich mit mir,\Nund werde mein kraft!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:01.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:04.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya! What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:14.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In this moment,\NI have gained the ultimate power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:19.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate…power?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:23.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For eons, I investigated\Nand researched ancient records,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:26.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And I had Ichinose search for it…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:28.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was able to track it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:33.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to the Department of Research\Nand Development…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:39.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The name of this original crest\Nis the Jokai Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:43.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is a crest that can purify\Nand erase everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:45.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jokai Crest…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:49.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is where the soul experiments
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:51.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that created\Nthe Bounts were done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:53.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:57.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When the experiment was\Ncanceled after the accident…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:20:00.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The incredible energy that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:03.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,made up the entire foundation\Nof the experiment in the Jokai Crest
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:04.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,was sealed away…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:06.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And now…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:10.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have become one with that energy…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:13.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:18.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It means that\NI can blow away Seireitei
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:22.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,at any time by releasing\Nthe energy of the Jokai Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:23.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:25.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Like I’d believe something\Nlike that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:28.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Believe what you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:31.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that anyone\Nshould believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:35.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Those eyes…he's serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:37.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:40.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:44.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if you attack me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:48.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll release the Jokai Crest\Nwhen you do…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:51.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Attack me if you dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:57.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the foolish people of Seireitei…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:59.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a one-day grace period.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:02.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Until then,\Ntremble in suspense!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:04.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:05.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:07.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:10.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If what he said was true…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:19.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:23.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my. It seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.29,0:21:29.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we were able to\Ncome here, thanks to that kid…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:33.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll thank him for that at least…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:38.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:16.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You always lament on\Nhow boring this town is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.17,0:22:20.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,…Searching for a place in the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.75,0:22:25.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The melody you hum is that\Nrusty, same old song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.43,0:22:29.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,…Rejecting any new song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:38.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're anxious because somewhere\Nin your heart, you believe in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.56,0:22:40.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, it's you;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.66,0:22:48.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That pain will eventually become\Na memory
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:50.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:57.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think, just feel,\Nlet your whole body tremble;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.65,0:22:59.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,future is you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.61,0:23:01.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, it's me;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.76,0:23:08.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're never alone, I'm right here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:11.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We should be as one;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:14.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you stumble, I don’t mind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.82,0:23:21.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell you now\Nabout the thing called love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.28,0:23:26.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya got away from us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.61,0:23:28.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I really should have come\Nin my gigai.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:30.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's a gigai that Master Mayuri\Nis using for his experiments…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.40,0:23:32.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in the Department of Research\Nand Development.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.64,0:23:33.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can borrow it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:35.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A squid-type, an octopus-type,\Nor a starfish-type.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.75,0:23:37.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which one would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.19,0:23:38.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:49.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers\NGolden after these messages!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.93,0:23:51.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.81,0:23:52.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.11,0:23:54.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:58.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? it's Mayuri Kurotsuchi!\NWhat's wrong? You look terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.34,0:23:59.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Carry me inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.05,0:24:02.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Should I carry you…here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:05.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Owww! Hey!\NYou're going to tear me apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.68,0:24:08.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then how should we carry you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.25,0:24:09.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By piggyback.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.65,0:24:13.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ready! Rock Paper Scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.72,0:24:14.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You two…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:14.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rock Paper Scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.87,0:24:15.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you don’t…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.90,0:24:15.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rock Paper Scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.94,0:24:16.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,…want me piggyback…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.96,0:24:16.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rock Paper Scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.85,0:24:17.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rock Paper Scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:18.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,…then just…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.01,0:24:19.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,…tell me straight out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.06,0:24:19.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rock Paper Scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.83,0:24:27.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,On my honor as a Quincy!